Class AdvisoriesResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hamweather.aeris.response.AerisFriendlyResponse
      • com.hamweather.aeris.response.AdvisoriesResponse

  • public class AdvisoriesResponse
extends AerisFriendlyResponse
    Object to make the advisories endpoint response more friendly to determine what parts of the AerisDataJSON have come back in the response.
